  rdfs:comment           "Imported from Reactome: https://reactome.org/content/detail/R-HSA-9033241" , "Entity Regulation Rule 3. The relation 'PEX2:PEX10:PEX12 monoubiquitinates PEX5L at cysteine-11' 'null' 'PEX1:PEX6:PEX26:ZFAND6 dissociates Ub:PEX5L and PEX7 from PEX14:PEX13:PEX2:PEX10:PEX12 and translocates PEX5L and PEX7 from the peroxisomal membrane to the cytosol' was inferred because:\n reaction1 has an output that is the enabler of reaction 2." ;
